('G3824','G','παλιγγενεσία','palingenesía','pal-ing-ghen-es-ee''-ah','','(spiritual) rebirth (the state or the act), i.e.  (figuratively) spiritual renovation; specially, Messianic  restoration',':--regeneration.'),
('G3825','G','πάλιν','pálin','pal''-in','','(adverbially) anew, i.e. (of place) back, (of time) once  more, or (conjunctionally) furthermore or on the other hand',':--again.'),
