('G5445','G','φύραμα','phýrama','foo''-ram-ah','','perhaps  akin to  through the idea of swelling in bulk), mean to knead; a  mass of dough',':--lump.'),
('G5446','G','φυσικός','physikós','foo-see-kos''','','"physical", i.e. (by implication) instinctive',':--natural.  Compare'),
