('G5449','G','φύσις','phýsis','foo''-sis','','growth (by germination or expansion), i.e. (by implication)  natural production (lineal descent); by extension, a genus or sort;  figuratively, native disposition, constitution or usage',':--(man-)kind,  nature(-al).'),
('G5450','G','φυσίωσις','physíōsis','foo-see''-o-sis','','inflation, i.e. (figuratively) haughtiness',':--swelling.'),
